      <title>Version 1.1</title>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[
        <h1>Important!</h1>
        <p><strong>Automatic updating process may fail</strong> under the versions below this.</p>
        <p>So, you have to <a href="http://oniatsu.github.io/HotSwitch/">donwload the latest HotSwitch</a> manually, and overwrite the HotSwitch at /Applications directory.</p>

        <h2>ChangeLog</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Fix showing window lists to add some window lists without title</li>
          <li>Fix the panel size opened first time on Yosemite</li>
          <li>Change a timing to hide the panel on switching</li>
          <li>Add a menu item to open HotSwitch panel</li>
          <li>Remove some OS X's default keyboard shortcuts</li>
        </ul>
        ]]>
